  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6570223">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6570223/" class="title-link">压缩一半或更多的篇幅可能会更好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6570223"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/70900110/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u70900110-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/70900110/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">白云无尽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-03-02"
      class="main-meta">2014-03-02 21:55:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6570223_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  用了10个月的时间，反复多次终于看完了这两本书。前两年看过王立群先生读史记的几本书，感觉还行，但这次王先生让我失望了。全书啰啰嗦嗦、絮絮叨叨，基本上没有自己的观点，即使有些归纳也属于八股式。如压缩一半或更多的篇幅，挤掉水份可能会好些。期待王先生有新作。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6570223_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6570223_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



